title: Skyway to Death (1974 TV Movie)
description:
An alcoholic aerial tramway operator is fired after being caught on the job intoxicated, and retaliates by sabotaging the car's cable.  His act of revenge leaves its passengers stuck 8500 feet in the air as a vicious storm approaches, threatening to weaken the already fragile cable.  

Strangely, I wanted to see this but had a hard time finding it.  Now I'm sharing the wealth.  I'm not sure where or what this was ripped from, but no DVD or (official) VHS version was ever released -- so be content that this exists.  If you enjoy films like the Towering Inferno this should be right up your alley.
